OL,3,CUnions not ruling out strike action as
OL,4,Cplan for education budget published
OL,6,FConcern has been expressed after
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's Education Minister
OL,8,Fpublished a budget plan to plug a
OL,9,Fprojected #1 billion-a-year funding
OL,10,Fgap.
OL,12,FPaul Givan's five-year budget strategy
OL,13,Fincludes proposals such as reducing
OL,14,Fthe number of schools in the region.
OL,16,FIt will also reform home to school
OL,17,Ftransport, school meals delivery, and
OL,18,F"reshape" special educational needs
OL,19,F(Sen) support in mainstream schools,
OL,20,Fas well as introducing a new model of
OL,21,Ffinancial management for schools.
