OL,3,CUnions not ruling out strike action as
OL,4,Cplan for education budget published
OL,6,FUnions haven't ruled out strike action
OL,7,Fover the proposals.
OL,9,FJanette Murdock from NIPSA said: "Next
OL,10,Fwe have to go to our members we'll be
OL,11,Ftaking advice from them and we will be
OL,12,Fdefending the cuts."
OL,14,FMr Givan described a system "under
OL,15,Fsevere and sustained strain". He said
OL,16,Fhis department's 2025-2026 budget is
OL,17,F#3.36 billion, more than #250 million
OL,18,Fshort of what is needed.
