OL,6,FHe added that based on projected
OL,7,Fbudget allocations, the gap between
OL,8,Ffunding available and spending
OL,9,Fforecasts widens to more than #0.8
OL,10,Fbillion by 2026/27 and more than #1.15
OL,11,Fbillion by 2028/29.
OL,13,F"Years of chronic underfunding and
OL,14,Flimited structural reform in service
OL,15,Fdelivery have combined to create a
OL,16,Ffinancial crisis in education," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
