OL,3,CUnions not ruling out strike action as
OL,4,Cplan for education budget published
OL,6,F"I will continue to make the strongest
OL,7,Fpossible case for sustained and
OL,8,Fincreased investment in our education
OL,9,Fsystem, but the numbers tell a stark
OL,10,Fstory. In the absence of significantly
OL,11,Fincreased funding, financial
OL,12,Fsustainability will require
OL,13,Fsignificant structural reform of the
OL,14,Feducation system."
OL,16,FMr Givan said its starting point was
OL,17,Fthat the classroom "must come first",
OL,18,Fbut that difficult choices would be
OL,19,Frequired.
