OL,6,F"My department's reform proposals
OL,7,Fhave, therefore, been guided by the
OL,8,Fclear principle of protecting teaching
OL,9,Fand learning while we put education on
OL,10,Fa sustainable financial footing.
OL,11,FDelivering this protection requires
OL,12,Fdifficult choices," he said.
OL,14,F"To be clear, we cannot close a
OL,15,Fbillion pound gap, or even
OL,16,Fmeaningfully reduce it through making
OL,17,Fmarginal efficiencies. Nor can we
OL,18,Fcontemplate largescale redundancies.
