OL,4,Cplan for education budget published
OL,6,F"Northern Ireland's education system
OL,7,Fis now at a critical turning point.
OL,8,FThe proposed reform programme offers a
OL,9,Fcredible and necessary roadmap to
OL,10,Fstabilise budgets, protect learning
OL,11,Fand build a sustainable, highquality
OL,12,Fsystem for the long-term."
OL,14,FHe added that decisions to deliver
OL,15,Freform "will not be easy and will
OL,16,Frequire political consensus".
OL,18,F"But the proposed budget allocation
OL,19,Fmakes them unavoidable," he said.
