OL,3,CUnions not ruling out strike action as
OL,4,Cplan for education budget published
OL,6,F"This reform programme is not about
OL,7,Ftemporary fixes. It is about reshaping
OL,8,Fthe system so it is stronger, more
OL,9,Fresilient and better equipped to
OL,10,Fdeliver excellent outcomes for every
OL,11,Fchild, now and for generations to
OL,12,Fcome."
OL,14,FThe proposals have been put out for
OL,15,Fpublic consultation.
OL,17,FOpposition education spokeswoman Cara
OL,18,FHunter said the "sweeping changes
OL,19,Fproposed" have "already caused real
OL,20,Fconcern among schools and parents".
