OL,4,Cplan for education budget published
OL,6,F"In the context of severe financial
OL,7,Fpressures across the department and
OL,8,Fthe wider Executive, and a changing
OL,9,Fschool landscape, it is clear that
OL,10,Freform is needed," she said.
OL,12,F"However, these proposals should not
OL,13,Fbe used in a game of brinkmanship
OL,14,Fbetween Minister Givan and the Finance
OL,15,FMinister.
OL,17,F"It is essential that the voices of
OL,18,Fschools, unions and parents are fully
OL,19,Fheard as part of this consultation.
